    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly so sad to let this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for someone else to enjoy this absolute gem. This car is in truly incredible shape\u2014honestly, it looks and feels like it just left the showroom floor! It\u2019s been babied since day one, kept tucked away in a garage, and there isn't a single blemish to be found. If you're looking for a ride that feels brand new without the brand-new price tag, this is the one. Come take a look, I promise you're going to fall in love!",
