    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is a true showroom-quality specimen, meticulously maintained to meet the highest standards. The exterior features a deep, mirror-like finish with zero imperfections, protected by a professional ceramic coating. Inside, the cabin remains in factory-fresh condition; the premium leather seats show no bolster wear, and every control retains its original tactile feel. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, with a comprehensive service history and an engine bay clean enough to display. From the pristine alloy wheels wrapped in fresh rubber to the untouched undercarriage, this car represents the pinnacle of its class. It is ready for the most discerning collector or enthusiast who demands nothing less than perfection.",
      "price": 48500.0,
