      "description": "This 997.2 Carrera S represents a masterclass in mechanical purity, featuring the coveted 3.8L naturally aspirated flat-six with Direct Fuel Injection (DFI). The drivetrain is anchored by a precise 6-speed manual transaxle and a factory mechanical limited-slip differential, ensuring optimal torque distribution and visceral driver engagement. The exterior retains its factory depth with zero paint meter deviations, while the undercarriage remains concours-clean, showing no signs of heat-cycling fatigue or fluid seepage. Equipped with Porsche Active Suspension Management (PASM) and a sport-tuned exhaust, the chassis dynamics are as sharp as the day it left Zuffenhausen. A comprehensive service file and a flawless DME report\u2014indicating zero over-revs in all ranges\u2014confirm that this high-revving powerplant has been maintained to the highest technical standards.",
